ins-007.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"180","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"300"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/18/1395162207109/Roy-Jenkins-008.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"228","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"380"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/18/1395162208672/Roy-Jenkins-009.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"276","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"460"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/18/1395162210020/Roy-Jenkins-010.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"372","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"620"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/18/1395162211368/Roy-Jenkins-011.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"1116","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"1860"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/18/1395162214043/Roy-Jenkins-012.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Jane Bown","altText":"Roy Jenkins","height":"1228","credit":"Jane Bown","caption":"'A back story worth flaunting' … Roy Jenkins Photograph: Jane Bown","width":"2047"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pic